=============================================================
Где посмотреть сырой LLM request/response

Смотри не data/reports/run_*.json, а именно vacancy log:

cat data/logs/vacancies/131294299/run_20260328_211045.json

Чтобы вытащить только LLM-часть:

python - <<'EOF'
import json
from pathlib import Path

p = Path("data/logs/vacancies/131294299/run_20260328_211045.json")
data = json.loads(p.read_text(encoding="utf-8"))
print(json.dumps(data.get("llm", []), ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))
EOF

Чтобы отдельно посмотреть raw request/response:

python - <<'EOF'
import json
from pathlib import Path

p = Path("data/logs/vacancies/131294299/run_20260328_211045.json")
data = json.loads(p.read_text(encoding="utf-8"))

for i, item in enumerate(data.get("llm", []), 1):
    print(f"\n=== LLM stage {i} request ===")
    print(json.dumps(item.get("debug", {}).get("request", {}), ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))
    print(f"\n=== LLM stage {i} response ===")
    print(json.dumps(item.get("debug", {}).get("response", {}), ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))
EOF
=========================


